Pindutin ang sumusunod na link upang gawing aktibo ang iyong user account:
%%s','Note: Neither of these options blocks access to your site &mdash; it is up to search engines to honor your request.'=>'Tandaan: Alinman sa mga opsiyon na ito ang maghahadlang ng access sa iyong site; Nasasaayon ito base sa mga search engine kung paparangalan ang iyong hiling. ','Howdy ###USERNAME###,

You recently clicked the \'Delete Site\' link on your site and filled in a
form on that page.

If you really want to delete your site, click the link below. You will not
be asked to confirm again so only click this link if you are absolutely certain:
